14:
Yahweh, commander of the angel armies has solemnly promised, using his own name,\q1 "Your cities will be filled with your enemies;
\q2 I will cause them to be like a swarm of locusts;
\q2 and they will shout triumphantly when they conquer your city."


\q1

19:
But the God of Israel is not like those idols;\q2 he is the one who created everything that exists;
\q1 we, the tribe of Israel, belong to him;
\q2 his name is Yahweh, commander of the angel armies.


\q1
